>Description:
On WinXp the following will make DrScheme hang:

 1. Save files as foo1.scm
 2. Save the same file as foo2.scm using "Save as..."
 3. Choose "Save as..." once more, right click on "foo1.scm"
    and choose "Delete".

This will make DrScheme hang.
